    your current item\n2                                             \u2014  Equip
    the metal bar                      \t\t\t\t               \t\t\t\t\t(banish ghosts
    up close)\n1                                            \u2014  Equip the magic
    wand  (once picked)        \t\t\t\t\t\t (cast spells from afar)\nR                                           
    \u2014  Read new spells onto your wand         \t\t\t\t                   (reload)\nLeft
    Shift                             \u2014  Sprint\nLeft Ctrl                             
    \u2014  Crouch\nSpace                                   \u2014  Jump\n\nPress
    Tab again to close"
